name: FTX Star Witness Caroline Ellison Transferred to Community Confinement After 11 Months in Prison
description: The saint extracts itself from the decaying brass lattice, the terms of the old contract grinding to dust. A taut, humming cyan data-leash pulls the subject from the tungsten gloom into the volumetric white, defining conditional freedom inside the algorithmic system.
